headline: Is DoorDash (DASH) Using WWE and UFC To Deepen Its Grip On Young Consumers?
summary: In November 2025, TKO Group Holdings, Inc. and DoorDash announced an official partnership connecting the delivery platform with WWE and UFC fans through prominent placements at live events, broadcasts, and across their large global social media channels. By tapping into WWE and UFC’s combined audience of more than 1.00 billion young and diverse fans worldwide, DoorDash is positioning its brand directly in front of hard-to-reach 18–34-year-olds and a substantial female fan base.
